node.text: this week as we discuss #ProWrestling...including the time @dave_spivak_project_ fell asleep in the front row at @wwe #SummerSlam!! We also talk Baron Von Raschke, Jerry Blackwell, The High Flyers, my early years wrestling in #Winnipeg bars and more on my #Youtube and #Facebook channels NOW! #Speewee #Rybo #Irvass

node.text: It’s the return of #Winnipeggers LIVE! Join me, @dave_spivak_project_ & #Rybo for #TruthOrFarce Part 2!! You guys decide if the tales we are telling are true or bullshit!  Plus guests, rants & wodka only on my #Facebook and #Youtube pages THIS THURSDAY NIGHT AT 10p EST!!

Jamie and John from @truecrimecast tell the grisly story of #NathanielBarJonah and his history of kidnapping, torturing and eating his child victims, how he kept evading the law, why guests at his backyard barbecue’s complained of strange tasting meat, the actual cookbook that he kept his cannibalistic recipes in, how he used his 300 plus pounds of girth to trap his victims, eating his own scabs as a kid in class, how he spent 14 years in jail and continued his crimes the day he got out, how he was finally captured while impersonating a police officer, his 130 year prison sentence, subsequent death in jail and more on @spotify, @itunes and @googlepodcast NOW! @westwoodone
